data.description: OWNER FINANCE OPTIONS AVAILABLE. 20% DOWN MOTIVATED SELLER.   Introducing an exquisite new listing in the highly sought-after Alamo Ranch community, nestled on the far west side of San Antonio, Texas. This captivating home boasts an impressive 2860 sq ft of living space and is ideally situated on a spacious corner lot. Impeccably maintained and move-in ready, this residence offers the epitome of comfort and style.    Featuring a thoughtful layout, all three bedrooms are conveniently located on the first floor, providing a seamless living experience. The upper level offers endless possibilities, with the potential for a fourth bedroom and additional space to suit your needs - whether it's a playroom, home gym, or entertainment area.    Indulge in the luxury of four full bathrooms, ensuring convenience for everyone. With a loft and an office, this home presents flexibility and versatility, accommodating your lifestyle effortlessly.    Crafted by Chesmar Homes in 2020, this property harmoniously blends modern design with quality construction. The Alamo Ranch neighborhood offers a host of amenities, from parks to shopping and dining, all within easy reach.    Don't miss out on this remarkable opportunity to own a stunning piece of Alamo Ranch. Schedule a showing today and envision the limitless possibilities that await in this Chesmar masterpiece.
